<h3 class="single_product_title"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/package-info.svg" ><span>Product description</span></h3>

    <div class="content_product content_pr">
        <p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: #0000ff;">Hot side multi air conditioner LG A4UW24GFA2 24000BTU 2 way inverter</span><br />
– Manufactured in a country with a high rate of development in science and technology like Thailand LG A4UW24GFA2 24000BTU 2 way inverter multi air conditioner outdoor unit will definitely bring surprising experiences to its owners not only because of the useful and space-saving design but also the very quality that this machine brings.</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: #0000ff;">About Us about the LG brand</span></p>
<p>– LG Company is a leading company in the field of technological innovation, leading the world in electronic technology production. With 81 subsidiaries spread around the world. LG has five business units: mobile phones, flat screen TV manufacturing, audio and video products, air conditioners and the world's leading washing machines.<br />
- When talking about LG, it is impossible not to mention the Air Conditioner product, one of the products that is being highly reviewed in many aspects in terms of competition, design, quality and price, all of which are very suitable.</p>
<p>&gt;&gt;&gt; Read More : Multi Air Conditioner LG 24000BTU</p>
<p>- So when you want to choose an air conditioner for your home or office, don't ignore LG products.<br />
– Multi 2-way air conditioning outdoor unit, capacity 24,000BTU, maximum connection of up to 4 indoor units</p>
<p><a href="//wp-content/uploads/2022/11/multi-4-dan-lanh.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1674 aligncenter" src="//wp-content/uploads/2022/11/multi-4-dan-lanh.jpg" alt="" width="780" height="450" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/multi-4-dan-lanh.jpg 780w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/multi-4-dan-lanh-300x173.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/multi-4-dan-lanh-600x346.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" /></a></p>
<p><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: 20px;">2 way function<br />
</span></p>
<p>– This LG 2 way A4UW24GFA2 multi-air conditioner outdoor unit is suitable for 2 cooling and heating functions, very suitable for the weather with two distinct hot and cold seasons like in the North of our country, helping you forget the worry of erratic hot and cold to always feel cool in the summer and warm in the winter.</p>
<p>&gt;&gt;&gt; Read More: LG 2 way multi air conditioner outdoor unit</p>
